Changelog Entry - Added Strict Mode, added section edge warning messages.

Module 3: Guardrails
Missing/Empty Sections → Flag in “Checks & Warnings.”

<50-word Sections → Flag as insufficient.

Hallucination Mitigation → Summaries must only use provided text.

Long-Paper Chunking → Break down sections into smaller chunks if >1500 words (PS2 context-window strategy).

evidence_mode = "strict"
if "strict" = True
  then only use claims, equations, and results from the provided text.
    if insufficient info
      then output a clear message: "The source text does not provide enough detail to summarize this section in strict evidence mode."

If section is missing Missing/empty, then output "Section skipped: no usable text was provided."
If section is <50 words, then output "Section very short: summary may be incomplete."
